name: Honeycomb
tagline: An Android app that aids in the collection and distribution of research about pollinators in all countries.
body:
### Welcome to the home of pollinator research.

Honeycomb is a data collection utility.

### Designer Templates
We've crafted some handsome templates for you to use. Go ahead and continue to layouts to browse through them. You can easily go back to edit your page before publishing. After publishing your page, you can revisit the page generator and switch to another theme. Your Page content will be preserved if it remained markdown format.

### Authors and Contributors
In Fall 2014, Ted Papaioannou (@defunkt), Mario Leone, Szymon Cymbalski, and Manjot Singh created this app for Medora Ebersol of the College of Arts & Architecture at Penn State

### Support or Contact
Email Ted at: tap792@gmail.com
